1
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,200
Hand over the ledger.

2
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:19,720
Hand over the ledger.

3
00:01:19,720 --> 00:01:20,580
Did you hear me?

4
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:23,000
Let me go,

5
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,120
and I'll give you the ledger.

6
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:25,560
Did I say I wouldn't let you go?

7
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,400
Did I say that?

8
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:27,640
Hand over the ledger.

9
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:29,400
I'll let you go right now.

10
00:01:29,440 --> 00:01:31,520
Haven't I said that enough over the years?

11
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:32,520
Did you ever let me go?

12
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:34,800
Don't you always find some excuse to keep me trapped?

13
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:35,600
Fine.

14
00:01:36,960 --> 00:01:39,289
I, Xiao Tianman, apologize to you. Happy?

15
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,200
Give me back the ledger now.

16
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:43,460
I promise I'll let you go this time. Okay?

17
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:46,120
Let me ask you, if I give you the ledger,

18
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,000
will I survive?

19
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,680
Will I make it out that door?

20
00:01:49,039 --> 00:01:50,500
You've got quite a temper.

21
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:52,520
I know you too well, Xiao Tianman.

22
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,320
What exactly do you want?

23
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:55,250
What do you want?

24
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:56,960
What do you want?

25
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,280
I want 500,000.

26
00:01:58,320 --> 00:02:00,640
How much? 500,000? 500,000?

27
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:02,570
Do you think you're worth 500,000?

28
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,880
Am I not worth 500,000?

29
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,039
Let me tell you,

30
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:11,160
Xiao Tianman, 500,000, not a penny less.

31
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,020
If you don't give me the money,

32
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:15,400
where the ledger will be tomorrow,

33
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:16,680
I can't say.

34
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:20,440
Come here.

35
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:23,079
Look at all these injuries on me.

36
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:25,320
How did I get them?

37
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,440
Wasn't it because of you?

38
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:29,640
You sent me to that man named Sun.

39
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:33,020
How much money did you make off me?

40
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,640
Do you think you earned that money yourself?

41
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,920
That was because of me.

42
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:40,200
Do you think Sun would help you without me?

43
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,760
I'm telling you,

44
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:45,360
you must give me the 500,000 today.

45
00:02:46,160 --> 00:02:47,600
I promise you, okay?

46
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:50,420
Just give me the ledger first.

47
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,480
In your dreams.

48
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:55,600
I hate being threatened.

49
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:57,920
Give me the ledger.

50
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,980
Give the ledger back to me.

51
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,920
You bitch.

52
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,120
Give me back the ledger.

53
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,120
Hand it over.

54
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:15,320
Give it back.

55
00:03:19,079 --> 00:03:21,400
Give it back! Give it back!

56
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,640
From now on,

57
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,960
we're in danger.

58
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,880
Until we bring down Xiao Tianman,

59
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:55,370
many people will be coming for this recorder.

60
00:03:57,079 --> 00:03:57,920
So remember,

61
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,560
if you two go out,

62
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,240
stick to crowded places.

63
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,840
Why don't we just give it to Gaoshan?

64
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:10,640
If Xiao Tianman finds out we have the recorder,

65
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:13,400
we're in danger every day we keep it.

66
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,200
Exactly.

67
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:18,130
Xiao Tianman will definitely retaliate.

68
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,720
So we have to give it to Gaoshan quickly.

69
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:24,160
We can only pray Gaoshan takes out Xiao Tianman soon.

70
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,420
The sooner, the safer.

71
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,290
There's no turning back for us.

72
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:32,730
We can't give it to Gaoshan.

73
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:36,290
Gaoshan is just like Xiao Tianman.

74
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,120
Then what do we do?

75
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:49,600
We'll give it to Situ.

76
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,240
Xie Lao'er.

77
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:22,480
Mr. Xiao.

78
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,720
Who touched this?

79
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,760
Who touched my drawer?

80
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:29,020
I don't know, Mr. Xiao.

81
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:30,040
I was drunk.

82
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,920
I'll teach you to get drunk!

83
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:32,760
Come here.

84
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:33,880
Who came in?

85
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,400
Tell me who entered my room.

86
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:36,440
Who was here?

87
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:38,360
Mr. Xiao, I was drunk and fell asleep.

88
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:40,020
I really don't know anything.

89
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:42,400
You fell asleep? You fell asleep?

90
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:44,040
Do I pay you to sleep?

91
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:44,720
I'll teach you to sleep!

92
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,440
Mr. Xiao, stop hitting me!

93
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:46,159
I'll teach you to sleep!

94
00:05:46,159 --> 00:05:47,360
Spare me this time.

95
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,600
Give me another chance.

96
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,320
Mr. Xiao.

97
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,330
Give me another chance.

98
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,280
Get up.

99
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:01,090
Where's the surveillance?

100
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:02,850
Go check the surveillance.

101
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:11,800
Jiang Xiaomei, you...

102
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,400
How dare you plot against me!

103
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:53,200
Brother, no one's here.

104
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:04,360
Yang Gang, how dare you play me!

105
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:15,920
Boss Xiao.

106
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:16,850
Sit. Have a seat.

107
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:17,840
Here.

108
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:25,680
I just sent Lao Er to the hospital.

109
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,120
He gave Yuan'er some more money.

110
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:31,930
You don't have to worry about the medical bills anymore.

111
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,880
Thank you, Boss Xiao.

112
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:38,440
Everything at the mine is going smoothly.

113
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,680
Don't worry about it.

114
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:42,060
I trust you to get things done.

115
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:47,400
I asked you here for something else.

116
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:50,640
What is it?

117
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,640
I got played.

118
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,480
Who?

119
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:03,680
Gao Shan.

120
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:05,880
And the three Yang brothers.

121
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:08,060
They stole something from me.

122
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:11,720
Yang Gang?

123
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,400
But, Brother,

124
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:16,160
how would Yang Gang dare steal from you?

125
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,640
What did he take?

126
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:19,960
A voice recorder.

127
00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:23,810
Is it important?

128
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,720
Very.

129
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:31,700
If I don't get that recorder back,

130
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,880
I'm a dead man.

131
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:42,799
Brother,

132
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,820
what exactly is on that recorder?

133
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,280
Fei, don't ask.

134
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:56,760
Knowing

135
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:00,720
won't do you any good.

136
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:06,960
Do me a favor.

137
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,400
At all costs,

138
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:12,560
get that recorder back for me.

139
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,080
Just the recording pen?

140
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:17,880
Right.

141
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:20,440
Just this recording pen.

142
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,980
Fei, don't worry about anything.

143
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,120
Okay?

144
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,440
Kidnap Yang Gang's mother.

145
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,680
If anything goes wrong,

146
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:34,000
I, Xiao Tianman, will cover for you.

147
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,660
I just want the recording pen.

148
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,580
Can you do it, brother?

149
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:48,200
Sure.

150
00:09:48,920 --> 00:09:49,720
Leave it to me.

151
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,640
Well then...

152
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,400
Brother.

153
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:59,440
Your mine is fine.

154
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,640
See Fei out.

155
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:25,920
Where is the patient from this bed?

156
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:27,080
She's been discharged.

157
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,080
Who authorized it?

158
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:28,920
I don't know.

159
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:50,360
Yang Gang.

160
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:52,620
Want to know where your mom is?

161
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,880
Exchange the recorder for her.
